f=Brand Studio/pulse/custom/social-content-calendar/SKILL.md · in=social-content-calendar pulse's planning spine: per-platform content calendar serializes weave's story chapters platform-native posts, lena's voice, deliberate cadence. implements three-layer hook design agreed 2026-07-07: **durable psychology** lives sibling `hook-writing` skill (static); **volatile platform knowledge** lives dated, refreshable playbooks (one platform, reviewed cadence); **ground truth** lives hooks register what actually worked *this* brand's audience, fed kai's numbers. Generic patterns propose; brand's data disposes. · p=Organic social fails two ways: posting randomly (no cadence, arc account noise) posting mechanically (same content cross-posted everywhere native nowhere). calendar fixes both: slot knows platform, format (from playbook), chapter (from weave's arc, labeled non-chapter), job. small business difference between "we post more" guilt system ships. · wu=Triggers: "content calendar," "what post," "plan week's/month's social," "serialize campaign," configured planning cadence. · st:/ Protocol=`Load: connected platforms (config) + each platform's playbook + brand voice guide + \· weave's current act/chapters + muse's content-mode ideas + hooks register \· -> Plan the period: slots per platform per cadence \· each slot = platform \· format (playbook) \· chapter ref (or labeled non-chapter) \· \· hook approach (register-first, then patterns) \· CTA/job` · h3:Phase Plan Period=connected platform (config's `connected_platforms` never assume platform business isn't on): pull playbook's current cadence norms formats, weave's current act (which chapters need telling), muse's validated content ideas, hooks register's what-works. Build calendar: one row slot. **Chapter mapping explicit** healthy mix carries arc forward while functional posts (offers, announcements) labeled non-chapter; spark tracks ratio. · h3:Phase Draft Platform-Native=slot: hook first (register's proven approaches audience get first shot; patterns fill gaps always adapted platform playbook, since YouTube cold-open LinkedIn first-line behave differently), body platform's format, lena's voice, through humanic-writing. **Cross-posting adaptation, copy-paste**: chapter becomes thread carousel Instagram, 40-second script TikTok one story, native executions. · h3:Phase Gate Publish=post gates spark (series batch-gate calendar defines series). Publishing platform connector write access exists; otherwise ready-to-post package (final copy pixel's assets posting notes) goes operator. Scheduled slots miss get rescheduled visibly, silently dropped. · h3:Phase 4 — Learn=kai's numbers land: post's hook approach format get outcome line hooks register; patterns decay get flagged; playbook refresh notes accumulate cadence review. self-annealing applied social calendar's next period plans evidence. · of=`## Calendar: [period] — [brand] \·  \· \| Slot \| Platform \| Date \| Format (playbook) \| Chapter / non-chapter \| Hook approach \| Job/CTA \| Status \| \·  \· Chapter ratio: [n chapter / m non-chapter] \· Gate: [batch refs] \· Publish: [connector/manual]` · pr=**Native platform it.** Adaptation playbook, never copy-paste distribution., **The register outranks pattern list.** brand's evidence beats generic psychology; generic patterns flagged craft heuristics (rule 0.6)., **Playbooks dated reviewed.** Undated platform advice stale advice hiding., **Chapters explicit, non-chapter labeled.** account tells brand's story admits isn't., **Missed slots reschedule visibly.**, **Real engagement bait only** manufactured controversy, fake urgency; lena's honesty rules apply social speed. · f=playbook platform start template's durable defaults, labeled provisional, date everything., connected platforms configured plan platforms operator names per-run; flag config gap., Empty hooks register (new brand) patterns carry load; register starts first period's outcomes., arc content labeled pre-arc (weave's rule); calendar still runs. · b:with Other Skills=`hook-writing` (sibling) psychology; playbooks platform layer; register evidence. skill orchestrates three., `community-engagement` (sibling) owns what happens after posting., **weave** owns chapters calendar series maps chapters; ledger tracks chapters, calendar tracks posts). **lena** owns voice humanic pass. **pixel** produces visuals slot. **muse** feeds validated ideas. **spark** gates. **kai** measures pulse never grades homework. **rio** owns paid amplification organic winners (handoff: register's proven posts rio's best creative candidates).